\begin_layout Plain Layout
Spot matching process.
 Buyers arrive at exogenous rate 
\begin_inset Formula $\beta$
\end_inset

, and contact available sellers.
 If rejected, a buyer leaves the platform.
 If accepted, the buyer forms a match which lasts for time 
\begin_inset Formula $\tau$
\end_inset

.
 After the time elapses, the buyer leaves the platform, and the seller returns
 to waiting.
 
