 An available seller receives requests at Poisson rate 
\begin_inset Formula $\beta_{A}$
\end_inset

.
 If a request is accepted, the seller becomes busy for time 
\begin_inset Formula $\tau$
\end_inset

 when he does not receive new requests.
 
\begin_inset CommandInset label
